      <title>Broadcom在股票滑梯后回收100亿美元的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/broadcom-to-buy-back-10-billion-in-shares-following-stock-slide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Broadcom Inc.是Apple Inc.和其他大型科技公司的半导体供应商，宣布了收购多达100亿美元股票的计划，称其对芯片行业仍然有信心。]]></description>
