    <item>
      <title>Kolanovic看到特朗普结束了关税“小丑表演”以节省股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/kolanovic-says-tariff-clown-show-is-the-trigger-for-trump-put</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统坚持认为，他永远不会改变将全球市场陷入动荡的贸易政策。对于马克·科拉诺维奇（Marko Kolanovic）来说，看来总统几乎陷入了压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/kolanovic-says-tariff-clown-show-is-the-trigger-for-trump-put</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 18:53:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场混乱使华尔街征集了资金应变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/market-chaos-puts-wall-street-on-alert-for-us-funding-strains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税导致投资者将美国资产倾销，投资者正在搜寻美元资金市场的破坏迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/market-chaos-puts-wall-street-on-alert-for-us-funding-strains</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 18:34:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普指示安全小组审查美国钢铁交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/trump-directs-security-panel-to-review-us-steel-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）下令对美国钢铁公司的潜在出售给Nippon Steel Corp.进行另一项审查，开门，修改其前任乔·拜登（Joe Biden）的决定，以阻止141亿美元的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/trump-directs-security-panel-to-review-us-steel-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 14:21:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EM股票擦除2025收益，因为关税燃料17年来最差的一天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/emerging-asian-currencies-slip-as-risk-off-extends-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易政策的影响继续在周一继续颠覆全球市场，新兴市场资产削弱了这一年的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/emerging-asian-currencies-slip-as-risk-off-extends-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 04:58:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着债券产量的激增，股票震惊的股票：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波动性的浪潮重新震撼了市场，股票，债券和商品被唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易战争的另一个头条新闻鞭打，这只会加强在投资和经济方面的云层。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/s-p-500-futures-slump-as-tariff-turmoil-deepens-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p 500帖子适度损失到野外关税波动的结束日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/us-stock-futures-tumble-with-trump-team-digging-in-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国的股票周一猛烈地挥舞着，消除了4％的跌幅超过3％，然后扭转方向略低，因为投资者对与唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易政策相关的头条新闻的反应略有下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/us-stock-futures-tumble-with-trump-team-digging-in-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 22:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
